                    (subtractTempRational.nominators.get(0) * -1));
    
            // add with its negative value
            return this.add(subtractTempRational);
    
        }
    
        private long getMultipliedValue(ArrayList&lt;Long&gt; longList) {
            Long mulResult = 1l;
            for (Long tempLong : longList) {
